#### Benefits of Computerized ASVAB
Background context: The computerized version offers several advantages over the paper-and-pencil format.

:p What are some benefits of taking the computerized ASVAB?
??x
Some benefits include:
- No risk of marking answers in the wrong space.
- Questions and options displayed on a screen, with key presses for responses.
- Difficulty adapts based on previous answers, maximizing AFQT score.
- Immediate scores calculated and printed.
- Quick determination of qualification status.

For code examples:
```java
public class ASVABTest {
    private boolean[] questionsAnswered;
    private int difficultyLevel;

    public void nextQuestion() {
        if (this.questionsAnswered.length > 0 && this.questionsAnswered[this.difficultyLevel]) {
            // Present a harder question
            ++this.difficultyLevel;
        } else {
            // Present an easier question
            --this.difficultyLevel;
        }
    }

    public void answerQuestion(int key) {
        if (key >= 'A' && key <= 'D') {
            this.questionsAnswered[this.difficultyLevel] = true;
        }
    }
}
```
