#### CAT-ASVAB Time Management
Background context: The CAT-ASVAB requires strict time management. Unlike the P&P version, you cannot revisit or change answers once a subtest's time is up.

:p How does time management work in the CAT-ASVAB?
??x
In the CAT-ASVAB, time management is crucial as you can't go back to previous questions or change your answers after completing each subtest. This means that every question should be given attention within its allocated time frame.

Code example for managing time:
```java
// Pseudocode for managing CAT-ASVAB time
void manageTime(int currentTime, int remainingTime) {
    // Logic to handle time management during the test
    if (remainingTime <= 0) {
        System.out.println("Time's up! Moving to next question.");
    } else {
        System.out.println("Time left: " + remainingTime);
    }
}
```
